<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IT Node | Enterprise Security Solution</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;500;700&display=swap');
        
        :root {
            --primary: #22d3ee;
            --bg: #030712;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: #f8fafc;
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .cyber-grid {
            background-image: radial-gradient(var(--primary) 0.5px, transparent 0.5px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            opacity: 0.15;
        }

        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2);
            position: relative;
        }

        .glass-panel::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3), transparent) border-box;
            -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) padding-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
            mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) padding-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
            -webkit-mask-composite: destination-out;
            mask-composite: exclude;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .glow-button {
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.4);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .glow-button:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.6);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .scan-line {
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--primary);
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            animation: moveScan 4s linear infinite;
            z-index: 20;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        @keyframes moveScan {
            0% { top: 0%; }
            100% { top: 100%; }
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.05);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased">

    <div class="fixed inset-0 cyber-grid z-0"></div>

    <nav class="relative z-50 flex justify-between items-center px-8 py-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-cyan-500 rounded flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class="fas fa-terminal text-black text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-widest text-cyan-400">IT_NODE</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
            <span class="hidden md:block text-[10px] font-mono text-cyan-800 tracking-[0.3em]">SECURE_CONNECTION_ESTABLISHED</span>
            <a href="https://t.me/it_node_secure_bot" class="text-xs font-bold border-b border-cyan-500 pb-1 hover:text-cyan-400 transition">LAUNCH_SYSTEM</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center pt-12 pb-24">
        
        <div>
            <div class="mb-6 inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded bg-cyan-500/10 border border-cyan-500/30 text-cyan-400 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest">
                System Status: Enterprise Ready
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-none">
                PRIVATE <br> <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600">INFRA_STRUCTURE</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-12 max-w-lg leading-relaxed font-light">
                Профессиональная сетевая инфраструктура для IT-специалистов. Стабильный доступ к глобальным репозиториям, облачным сервисам и инструментам разработки.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-8">
                <a href="https://t.me/it_node_secure_bot" class="glow-button bg-cyan-500 text-black px-10 py-5 rounded font-black uppercase tracking-tighter transition-all">
                    Получить доступ_
                </a>
                <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase leading-loose">
                    Encryption: VLESS + TLS 1.3 <br>
                    Uptime: 99.9% / Cluster: DE_NL_US
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <div class="scan-line"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8">
                    <span class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan-500 tracking-widest uppercase">> Network_Audit</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] bg-red-500/20 text-red-500 px-2 py-1 rounded animate-pulse">VULNERABLE</span>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-6 font-mono text-sm">
                    <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
                        <span class="text-gray-500">Source_IP:</span>
                        <span id="ip" class="text-red-400">Scanning...</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
                        <span class="text-gray-500">Node_Location:</span>
                        <span id="loc" class="text-red-400">Exposed</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
                        <span class="text-gray-500">Security_Protocol:</span>
                        <span class="text-red-400">None / Cleartext</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button onclick="fixSecurity()" id="fix-btn" class="w-full mt-10 py-4 border border-cyan-500/50 text-cyan-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-cyan-500 hover:text-black transition-all">
                    Patch Vulnerabilities_
                </button>

                <div id="success-msg" class="hidden mt-6 p-4 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 text-green-400 text-[10px] font-mono leading-relaxed">
                    [OK] Система перенаправлена через защищенный узел Private IT Node. Данные зашифрованы. Глобальные ресурсы доступны.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t border-white/5">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="feature-card glass-panel p-6 rounded-xl transition">
                <i class="fas fa-lock text-cyan-500 mb-4"></i>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Защита данных</h4>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Шифрование корпоративного уровня для защиты ваших паролей и транзакций в публичных сетях.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card glass-panel p-6 rounded-xl transition">
                <i class="fas fa-terminal text-cyan-500 mb-4"></i>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Для разработчиков</h4>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Бесперебойный доступ к Docker Hub, NPM, GitHub и другим критически важным сервисам.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card glass-panel p-6 rounded-xl transition">
                <i class="fas fa-globe text-cyan-500 mb-4"></i>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Глобальная сеть</h4>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Узлы в ключевых дата-центрах мира с минимальной задержкой (latency < 40ms).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card glass-panel p-6 rounded-xl transition">
                <i class="fas fa-user-shield text-cyan-500 mb-4"></i>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Приватность</h4>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Мы соблюдаем строгую политику минимизации данных. Ваши действия — это ваша личная информация.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-16 text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8">
        <div class="max-w-md text-center md:text-left">
            PRIVATE IT NODE IS A SECURITY TOOLSET. WE DO NOT CONDONE ILLEGAL ACTIVITY. USERS ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR COMPLIANCE WITH LOCAL LAWS.
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-8">
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-cyan-500 transition uppercase">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-cyan-500 transition uppercase">ToS</a>
            <a href="https://t.me/it_node_secure_bot" class="text-cyan-500 transition uppercase font-bold">Support_Bot</a>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Детектор IP (имитация для примера)
        setTimeout(() => {
            document.getElementById('ip').innerText = '178.154.XXX.XX';
            document.getElementById('loc').innerText = 'RUSSIA / MOSCOW';
        }, 1200);

        function fixSecurity() {
            const btn = document.getElementById('fix-btn');
            const msg = document.getElementById('success-msg');
            
            btn.innerHTML = '<i class="fas fa-circle-notch animate-spin"></i> PATCHING...';
            
            setTimeout(() => {
                btn.style.display = 'none';
                msg.classList.remove('hidden');
                document.getElementById('ip').innerText = 'HIDDEN / ENCRYPTED';
                document.getElementById('loc').innerText = 'NETHERLANDS / AMSTERDAM';
                document.getElementById('ip').classList.replace('text-red-400', 'text-green-400');
                document.getElementById('loc').classList.replace('text-red-400', 'text-green-400');
            }, 2000);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
